data.description: This move in ready split floor-plan 3 bedroom 2 bath home is waiting for a new owner! Tucked in a great culdesac location on a premium sized lot. You will appreciate the low maintenance landscaping and extended covered East facing rear patio. Perfectly shaded for afternoon barbecues! A 4 foot extension on the garage adds more room for toys without having to park outside. The inside is just as great with 10' high ceilings, 8' raised panel interior doors and a tile surround corner fireplace. Granite counter tops in the kitchen with subway tiled backsplash all around. The Primary Bedroom offers black-out shades for the late sleeper, a large walk-in closet, dual sink vanity and a walk-in shower with dual shower heads.
